    name: 'Captain James Morrison',
    term: '2023-2025',
    email: 'commodore@scyc.co.uk',
    bio: 'An experienced offshore sailor with over 30 years of sailing experience. James has competed in numerous national championships and brings extensive leadership experience to the role.',
